name: Nifty Tree #16
description: Nifty Tree #16 Phase 0 - The sixteenth Nifty Tree minting on Tezos chain. Nifty Trees first collection minted on Ethereum. This initial collection is available for trading with the Alpha release of www.niftytrees.com for the 7th U.S. National Bonsai Exhibition in Rochester, New York USA. Nifty Trees provides a digital representation of bonsai art. As we move into a digital information age, we offer a collection of bonsai art in the form of NFTs.
